@node "Audio" "Audio"

 AUDIO

If you selected the audio, Dialer will produce the telephone tones directly
by the standard audio of the Amiga. Pick your receiver up and put it near
the speaker of you monitor, television or hi-fi (if you have it), then let
Dialer dial the number... and it's all right: the number is dialed!!

Easy and funny, isn't it?
@endnode

@node "Modem" "Modem"

 MODEM

If you select the modem, Dialer will use it to dial the numbers. You must be
sure that your modem is turned on and that the serial device is free.

As soon as the modem has dialed the number, you can pick your telephone
receiver and hit a key.
@endnode

